snippet.textDisplay: Four Tet has a beautiful unique sound and this set is sick shit! Unfortunately his recent live show in Portland OR (5/4) was a major disappointment. He hardly played any original content, it sounded as if he was playing a mixtape he compiled from other peoples music, w/minor bass and beats added; the crowd seemed awfully bored with the status quo DJ club music set. There were no lights or stage projections, nor merch. It was a very sad night for us.
